e PvPed (an exception or two exsists). <br><br>Only recourse outside calling the staff on someone blocking a passage or training NPC's is to ALSO engage in that practice. Can we say Griefer paradise? The rules are clear and have a very clearly defined reason for exsisting.<br><br>So to answer the question about is it roleplaying to train Guards on other players..... NO, Verant has said that it is not, and they own, run and control the game. At least in Norrath. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=361.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=361.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=361.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=361.topic&start=81&stop=100>5</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=361.topic&start=101&stop=120>6</a><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showMessageRange?topicID=361.topic&start=121&stop=122>7</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showPrevMessage?topicID=361.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showNextMessage?topicID=361.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=361.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.threadControl?topicID=361.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Command